						<summary>

						<p>On a slab in front of the Mādhavasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>The record is dated in <hi rend="italic">Kīlaka, Āśvija,</hi> śu. 15; Written in late characters.</p>						

						<p>Records the receipt of the principal with interest amounting to <hi rend="italic">(9(1/2) rēkha-gadyas),</hi> issued by Nadala-yallappa to Mālakoṇḍa Timmarāju and states that the loan deed was deemed cancelled wherever it was.</p>						

